LOMBARDI & STREICHER GENERELLE OPEN-SOURCE LIZENZ

Any program licensed under the LOMBARDI & STREICHER GENERELLE OPEN-SOURCE LIZENZ may be used for free,
changed in a way to fit the user's demands, and may be redistributed without credit. Redistributed software may be charged for. *2)
The creator of the software does not need to provide any kind of warranty and any programs may be used at user's own risk.

1) DISTRIBUTION OF SOFTWARE
Users aquiring software licensed under the LOMBARDI & STREICHER GENERELLE OPEN-SOURCE LIZENZ must be able to get the source code.

2) REDISTRIBUTION OF SOFTWARE
Software can be redistributed as long as software code is changed. Software based off of software that is charged for, must also be charged for to avoid a monopoly.
